    dc:date "2022" ;
    dc:title "Viola ornata and Viola longibracteolata (Violaceae, subgen. Neoandinium), two rare, new rosulate species from southern Peru" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7270464>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7270468>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7270472>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7270478> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7270464>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Viola ornata. A. Mature rosette from above. B. Leaf (adaxial view). C. Detail of the hyaline ciliate hairs on leaf margins. D. Leaf (abaxial view). E. Pedicel and flower. F. Dissection of calyx showing sepals: superior sepal central. G. Detail of marginal cilium. H. Bracteole, showing three ciliate wings. I. Bracteoles cross sections (basal and apical). J. Upper view of inferior petal. K. Side view of the inferior petal showing retrorse spur. L. Lateral petal. M. Superior petal. N. Front view of style head. O. Style head and crest at tip of geniculate style branch above ovary. P. Inferior stamen with slender nectar spur and connective scale above." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7270464/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7270468>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Viola ornata. A. Habitat in the mountain summits near Yunga Town (elev. 4970 m). B. Solitary rosettes. C. Details of flowering. D. Details of leaf (adaxial view) showing ciliate margin. Photos: A and D by D.B. Montesinos; B and C by H. Trinidad." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7270468/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7270472>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. A. Solitary rosettes of Viola ornata in the mountain summits near Tassa Town (elev. 4705 m). B. Multiple rosettes with detail of the flowers of Viola ornata in the mountain summits near Ichuña. 4790 m. Photos: A by M. Sheader; B by H. Trinidad." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7270472/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7270478>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Distribution map of Viola ornata and Viola longibracteolata." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7270478/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

